<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Privacy Policy</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f4f7f8;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .container:hover {
      background-color: #eaffea; /* light green on hover */
    }

    .page-title {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.8em;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      color: #3498db;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-top: 25px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .bottom-center {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 40px auto;
    }

    .back-btn {
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .back-btn:hover {
      background-color: #27ae60; /* green on hover */
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .page-title {
        font-size: 2em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>At <strong>FoodSave</strong>, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Email Address:</strong> when you subscribe to our newsletter or updates.</li>
      <li><strong>Log Data:</strong> such as your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and time/date of visits.</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> to enhance user experience and track usage patterns.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your information is used to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Send newsletters and updates (if you subscribed).</li>
      <li>Improve our website based on user behavior.</li>
      <li>Monitor and analyze usage to enhance performance.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to others. We may share your information with trusted third-party services that help us operate the site, as long as they agree to keep this information confidential.</p>

    <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access or request a copy of your data.</li>
      <li>Request corrections or deletion of your personal information.</li>
      <li>Unsubscribe from newsletters at any time.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Security</h2>
    <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures to protect your personal information.</p>

    <h2>6. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>Our website may contain links to external sites that we do not operate. We are not responsible for their privacy practices.</p>

    <h2>7. Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with a revised date.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:support@foodsave.org">support@foodsave.org</a></p>

    <p><em>Last Updated: April 20, 2025</em></p>
